Hi! This is the contact mailer. I'm forwarding an incoming contact from the website.

Name: <%= @contact.name %>
Email: <%= @contact.email %>
<% if @contact.user_id && user = User.find_by_id(@contact.user_id) %>
  User: <%= user.at_name %> <%= user_url(user) %>
<% end %>
Subject: <%= @contact.subject %>

IP address: <%= @contact.ip %>
Referer: <%= @contact.referer %>
UserAgent: <%= @contact.useragent %>

Message:
<%= @contact.message %>

